        "I": "UI_Activity_MonsterChess_Monster_02",
        "D": "不同的交战单位之间存在一定的压制关系：<br>能造成<color style='color:#FFCC33'>范围伤害#的单位，面对<color style='color:#FFCC33'>小队#单位时具有显著优势。<br><color style='color:#FFCC33'>近战#单位压制<color style='color:#FFCC33'>远程#单位，<color style='color:#FFCC33'>远程#单位压制<color style='color:#FFCC33'>空中#单位，<color style='color:#FFCC33'>空中#单位压制<color style='color:#FFCC33'>近战#单位。"
